  <brief_title>Iron Overload Assesment in Sickle Cell Anemia and Sickle Cell Thalassemia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical and Laboratory Assessment of Iron Overload in Sickle Cell Anemia and Sickle Cell Thalassemia Using T2* Cardiac MRI.</official_title>
